> +#ifdef __ASSEMBLY__
Why add assembly condition? We only want this if CONFIG_FUNCTION_TRACER 
is enabled, right?  We could combine it with the current #ifndef inside 
the CONFIG_FUNCTION_TRACER. But I would make do:
#ifdef __ASSEMBLY__
<your stuff>
#else
< C stuff >
#endif
-- Steve
